      "span_text": "The ß-GLU staining was assayed as described by [CITATION_1] ; the sections were immersed in 0.1 M Na acetate-acetic acid buffer pH 4.5, containing 0.3 mg/ml Fast-Red GG (Sigma, F-7013) and 0.28 mg/ml naphthol AS-BI N-acetyl-ß-D-glucuronic acid (Sigma, N-1875) for 3h at 37°C."
